Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.36,Default,Inuyasha,0,0,0,,คาโงเมะ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.15,Default,Inuyasha,0,0,0,,พวกนั้นมาแล้ว!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.03,Default,Kagome Higurashi,0,0,0,,อื้อ
